dataIdInfo.idAbs:
This file represents the collection of many scenic byways that are found within the United States. Deemed "scenic" by some government entity, and can be seen on www.byways.org

For more information about the byways project and designation criterion please see www.byways.org.
dataIdInfo.idCredit: The roads depicted have been extracted from from 2005 US Streets as available from the US Census Bureau or traced from Google.com online mapping tools.
